title: MD COVID-19 Data Dashboard
description: This dashboard illustrates the total confirmed cases, total recovered cases, and total cases resulting in death of COVID-19 in the state of Maryland, by county. It is manually updated by the Maryland Emergency Management Agency (MEMA) with data published by the Governor's office and the Maryland Department of Health (MDH).
licenseInfo: This map is for planning purposes only. MEMA does not guarantee the accuracy of any forecast or predictive elements.
